T|Hour|2|Diagnosis: The status is unchanged from yesterday, which is itself the signal: no forward progress on the ct-path items that unlock ka's fn. The sequencing dependency remains:
T|Hour|3|fx → runway al + pricing md recommendation (HRB-002)
T|Hour|4|Stark → pricing approval
T|Hour|5|dv → trial-to-paid funnel (HRB-001)
