T|Cros|7|Stark's highest-leverage single action this week: cp .env.example to .env.local on the production dpl, fill in the sb credentials, and trigger one IG snapshot. That one action — maybe 10 minutes — unlocks ka, ro, nt, and fx simultaneously for nz, and sets the pattern for hb when its time comes.
